{"ja531:0.1":"Jataka ","ja531:0.2":"Sattatinipata ","ja531:0.3":"Kusavagga ","ja531:0.4":"1. Kusajataka ","ja531:1.1":"“Idam te rattham sadhanam sayoggam, ","ja531:1.2":"Sakayuram sabbakamupapannam; ","ja531:1.3":"Idam te rajjam anusasa amma, ","ja531:1.4":"Gacchamaham yattha piya pabhavati”. ","ja531:2.1":"“Anujjubhutena haram mahantam, ","ja531:2.2":"Diva ca ratto ca nisithakale; ","ja531:2.3":"Patigaccha tvam khippam kusavatim kusa, ","ja531:2.4":"Nicchami dubbannamaham vasantam”. ","ja531:3.1":"“Naham gamissami ito kusavatim, ","ja531:3.2":"Pabhavati vannapalobhito tava; ","ja531:3.3":"Ramami maddassa niketaramme, ","ja531:3.4":"Hitvana rattham tava dassane rato. ","ja531:4.1":"Pabhavati vannapalobhito tava, ","ja531:4.2":"Sammulharupo vicarami medinim; ","ja531:4.3":"Disam na janami kutomhi agato, ","ja531:4.4":"Tayamhi matto migamandalocane. ","ja531:5.1":"Suvannaciravasane, ","ja531:5.2":"jatarupasumekhale; ","ja531:5.3":"Sussoni tava kama hi, ","ja531:5.4":"naham rajjena matthiko”. ","ja531:6.1":"“Abbhuti tassa bho hoti, ","ja531:6.2":"yo anicchantamicchati; ","ja531:6.3":"Akamam raja kamesi, ","ja531:6.4":"akantam kantumicchasi”. ","ja531:7.1":"“Akamam va sakamam va, ","ja531:7.2":"yo naro labhate piyam; ","ja531:7.3":"Labhamettha pasamsama, ","ja531:7.4":"alabho tattha papako”. ","ja531:8.1":"“Pasanasaram khanasi, ","ja531:8.2":"kanikarassa daruna; ","ja531:8.3":"Vatam jalena badhesi, ","ja531:8.4":"yo anicchantamicchasi”. ","ja531:9.1":"“Pasano nuna te hadaye, ","ja531:9.2":"ohito mudulakkhane; ","ja531:9.3":"Yo te satam na vindami, ","ja531:9.4":"tirojanapadagato. ","ja531:10.1":"Yada mam bhakutim katva, ","ja531:10.2":"rajaputti udikkhati; ","ja531:10.3":"Alariko tada homi, ","ja531:10.4":"ranno maddassantepure. ","ja531:11.1":"Yada umhayamana mam, ","ja531:11.2":"rajaputti udikkhati; ","ja531:11.3":"Nalariko tada homi, ","ja531:11.4":"raja homi tada kuso”. ","ja531:12.1":"“Sace hi vacanam saccam, ","ja531:12.2":"nemittanam bhavissati; ","ja531:12.3":"Neva me tvam pati assa, ","ja531:12.4":"kamam chindantu sattadha”. ","ja531:13.1":"“Sace hi vacanam saccam, ","ja531:13.2":"annesam yadi va mamam; ","ja531:13.3":"Neva tuyham pati atthi, ","ja531:13.4":"anno sihassara kusa”. ","ja531:14.1":"“Nekkham givam te karessam, ","ja531:14.2":"patva khujje kusavatim; ","ja531:14.3":"Sace mam naganasuru, ","ja531:14.4":"olokeyya pabhavati. ","ja531:15.1":"Nekkham givam te karessam, ","ja531:15.2":"patva khujje kusavatim; ","ja531:15.3":"Sace mam naganasuru, ","ja531:15.4":"alapeyya pabhavati. ","ja531:16.1":"Nekkham givam te karessam, ","ja531:16.2":"patva khujje kusavatim; ","ja531:16.3":"Sace mam naganasuru, ","ja531:16.4":"umhayeyya pabhavati. ","ja531:17.1":"Nekkham givam te karessam, ","ja531:17.2":"patva khujje kusavatim; ","ja531:17.3":"Sace mam naganasuru, ","ja531:17.4":"pamhayeyya pabhavati. ","ja531:18.1":"Nekkham givam te karessam, ","ja531:18.2":"patva khujje kusavatim; ","ja531:18.3":"Sace mam naganasuru, ","ja531:18.4":"panihi upasamphuse”. ","ja531:19.1":"“Na hi nunayam rajaputti, ","ja531:19.2":"kuse satampi vindati; ","ja531:19.3":"Alarike bhate pose, ","ja531:19.4":"vetanena anatthike”. ","ja531:20.1":"“Na hi nunayam sa khujja, ","ja531:20.2":"labhati jivhaya chedanam; ","ja531:20.3":"Sunisitena satthena, ","ja531:20.4":"evam dubbhasitam bhanam”. ","ja531:21.1":"“Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:21.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:21.3":"Mahayasoti katvana, ","ja531:21.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:22.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:22.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:22.3":"Mahaddhanoti katvana, ","ja531:22.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:23.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:23.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:23.3":"Mahabbaloti katvana, ","ja531:23.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:24.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:24.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:24.3":"Maharatthoti katvana, ","ja531:24.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:25.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:25.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:25.3":"Maharajati katvana, ","ja531:25.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:26.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:26.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:26.3":"Sihassaroti katvana, ","ja531:26.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:27.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:27.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:27.3":"Vaggussaroti katvana, ","ja531:27.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:28.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:28.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:28.3":"Bindussaroti katvana, ","ja531:28.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:29.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:29.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:29.3":"Manjussaroti katvana, ","ja531:29.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:30.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:30.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:30.3":"Madhussaroti katvana, ","ja531:30.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:31.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:31.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:31.3":"Satasippoti katvana, ","ja531:31.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:32.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:32.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:32.3":"Khattiyotipi katvana, ","ja531:32.4":"karassu rucire piyam. ","ja531:33.1":"Ma nam rupena pamesi, ","ja531:33.2":"arohena pabhavati; ","ja531:33.3":"Kusarajati katvana, ","ja531:33.4":"karassu rucire piyam”. ","ja531:34.1":"“Ete naga upatthaddha, ","ja531:34.2":"sabbe titthanti vammita; ","ja531:34.3":"Pura maddanti pakaram, ","ja531:34.4":"anentetam pabhavatim”. ","ja531:35.1":"“Satta bile karitvana, ","ja531:35.2":"ahametam pabhavatim; ","ja531:35.3":"Khattiyanam padassami, ","ja531:35.4":"ye mam hantum idhagata”. ","ja531:36.1":"“Avutthahi rajaputti, ","ja531:36.2":"sama koseyyavasini; ","ja531:36.3":"Assupunnehi nettehi, ","ja531:36.4":"dasiganapurakkhata”. ","ja531:37.1":"“Tam nuna kakkupanisevitam mukham, ","ja531:37.2":"Adasadantatharupaccavekkhitam; ","ja531:37.3":"Subham sunettam virajam ananganam, ","ja531:37.4":"Chuddham vane thassati khattiyehi. ","ja531:38.1":"Te nuna me asite vellitagge, ","ja531:38.2":"Kese mudu candanasaralitte; ","ja531:38.3":"Samakule sivathikaya majjhe, ","ja531:38.4":"Padehi gijjha parikaddhissanti. ","ja531:39.1":"Ta nuna me tambanakha suloma, ","ja531:39.2":"Baha mudu candanasaralitta; ","ja531:39.3":"Chinna vane ujjhita khattiyehi, ","ja531:39.4":"Gayha dhanko gacchati yenakamam. ","ja531:40.1":"Te nuna talupanibhe alambe, ","ja531:40.2":"Nisevite kasikacandanena; ","ja531:40.3":"Thanesu me lambissati singalo, ","ja531:40.4":"Matuva putto taruno tanujo. ","ja531:41.1":"Tam nuna sonim puthulam sukottitam, ","ja531:41.2":"Nisevitam kancanamekhalahi; ","ja531:41.3":"Chinnam vane khattiyehi avattham, ","ja531:41.4":"Singalasangha parikaddhissanti. ","ja531:42.1":"Sona dhanka singala ca, ","ja531:42.2":"ye canne santi dathino; ","ja531:42.3":"Ajara nuna hessanti, ","ja531:42.4":"bhakkhayitva pabhavatim. ","ja531:43.1":"Sace mamsani harimsu, ","ja531:43.2":"khattiya duragamino; ","ja531:43.3":"Atthini amma yacitva, ","ja531:43.4":"anupathe dahatha nam. ","ja531:44.1":"Khettani amma karetva, ","ja531:44.2":"kanikarettha ropaya; ","ja531:44.3":"Yada te pupphita assu, ","ja531:44.4":"hemantanam himaccaye; ","ja531:44.5":"Sareyyatha mamam amma, ","ja531:44.6":"evamvanna pabhavati”. ","ja531:45.1":"“Tassa mata udatthasi, ","ja531:45.2":"khattiya devavannini; ","ja531:45.3":"Disva asinca sunanca, ","ja531:45.4":"ranno maddassantepure”. ","ja531:46.1":"“Imina nuna asina, ","ja531:46.2":"susannam tanumajjhimam; ","ja531:46.3":"Dhitaram madda hantvana, ","ja531:46.4":"khattiyanam padassasi. ","ja531:47.1":"Na me akasi vacanam, ","ja531:47.2":"atthakamaya puttike; ","ja531:47.3":"Sajja lohitasanchanna, ","ja531:47.4":"gacchasi yamasadhanam. ","ja531:48.1":"Evamapajjati poso, ","ja531:48.2":"papiyanca nigacchati; ","ja531:48.3":"Yo ve hitanam vacanam, ","ja531:48.4":"na karoti atthadassinam. ","ja531:49.1":"Sace ca ajja dharesi, ","ja531:49.2":"kumaram carudassanam; ","ja531:49.3":"Kusena jatam khattiyam, ","ja531:49.4":"suvannamanimekhalam; ","ja531:49.5":"Pujitam natisanghehi, ","ja531:49.6":"na gacchasi yamakkhayam. ","ja531:50.1":"Yatthassu bheri nadati, ","ja531:50.2":"kunjaro ca nikujati; ","ja531:50.3":"Khattiyanam kule bhadde, ","ja531:50.4":"kim nu sukhataram tato. ","ja531:51.1":"Asso ca sisati dvare, ","ja531:51.2":"kumaro uparodati; ","ja531:51.3":"Khattiyanam kule bhadde, ","ja531:51.4":"kim nu sukhataram tato. ","ja531:52.1":"Mayurakoncabhirude, ","ja531:52.2":"kokilabhinikujite; ","ja531:52.3":"Khattiyanam kule bhadde, ","ja531:52.4":"kim nu sukhataram tato”. ","ja531:53.1":"“Kaham nu so sattumaddano, ","ja531:53.2":"pararatthappamaddano; ","ja531:53.3":"Kuso solarapannano, ","ja531:53.4":"yo no dukkha pamocaye”. ","ja531:54.1":"“Idheva so sattumaddano, ","ja531:54.2":"pararatthappamaddano; ","ja531:54.3":"Kuso solarapannano, ","ja531:54.4":"yo te sabbe vadhissati”. ","ja531:55.1":"“Ummattika nu bhanasi, ","ja531:55.2":"Andhabala pabhasasi; ","ja531:55.3":"Kuso ce agato assa, ","ja531:55.4":"Kim na janemu tam mayam”. ","ja531:56.1":"“Eso alariko poso, ","ja531:56.2":"kumaripuramantare; ","ja531:56.3":"Dalham katvana samvellim, ","ja531:56.4":"kumbhim dhovati onato”. ","ja531:57.1":"“Veni tvamasi candali, ","ja531:57.2":"adusi kulagandhini; ","ja531:57.3":"Katham maddakule jata, ","ja531:57.4":"dasam kayirasi kamukam”. ","ja531:58.1":"“Namhi veni na candali, ","ja531:58.2":"na camhi kulagandhini; ","ja531:58.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:58.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi”. ","ja531:59.1":"“Yo brahmanasahassani, ","ja531:59.2":"sada bhojeti visatim; ","ja531:59.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:59.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi. ","ja531:60.1":"Yassa nagasahassani, ","ja531:60.2":"sada yojenti visatim; ","ja531:60.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:60.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi. ","ja531:61.1":"Yassa assasahassani, ","ja531:61.2":"sada yojenti visatim; ","ja531:61.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:61.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi. ","ja531:62.1":"Yassa rathasahassani, ","ja531:62.2":"sada yojenti visatim; ","ja531:62.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:62.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi. ","ja531:63.1":"Yassa usabhasahassani, ","ja531:63.2":"sada yojenti visatim; ","ja531:63.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:63.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi. ","ja531:64.1":"Yassa dhenusahassani, ","ja531:64.2":"sada duhanti visatim; ","ja531:64.3":"Okkakaputto bhaddante, ","ja531:64.4":"tvam nu dasoti mannasi”. ","ja531:65.1":"“Taggha te dukkatam bale, ","ja531:65.2":"yam khattiyam mahabbalam; ","ja531:65.3":"Nagam mandukavannena, ","ja531:65.4":"na nam akkhasidhagatam”. ","ja531:66.1":"“Aparadham maharaja, ","ja531:66.2":"tvam no khama rathesabha; ","ja531:66.3":"Yam tam annatavesena, ","ja531:66.4":"nannasimha idhagatam”. ","ja531:67.1":"“Madisassa na tam channam, ","ja531:67.2":"yoham alariko bhave; ","ja531:67.3":"Tvanneva me pasidassu, ","ja531:67.4":"natthi te deva dukkatam”. ","ja531:68.1":"“Gaccha bale khamapehi, ","ja531:68.2":"kusarajam mahabbalam; ","ja531:68.3":"Khamapito kuso raja, ","ja531:68.4":"so te dassati jivitam”. ","ja531:69.1":"“Pitussa vacanam sutva, ","ja531:69.2":"devavanni pabhavati; ","ja531:69.3":"Sirasa aggahi pade, ","ja531:69.4":"kusarajam mahabbalam”. ","ja531:70.1":"“Yama ratyo atikkanta, ","ja531:70.2":"tama deva taya vina; ","ja531:70.3":"Vande te sirasa pade, ","ja531:70.4":"ma me kujjha rathesabha. ","ja531:71.1":"Sabbam te patijanami, ","ja531:71.2":"maharaja sunohi me; ","ja531:71.3":"Na capi appiyam tuyham, ","ja531:71.4":"kareyyami aham puna. ","ja531:72.1":"Evance yacamanaya, ","ja531:72.2":"vacanam me na kahasi; ","ja531:72.3":"Idani mam tato hantva, ","ja531:72.4":"khattiyanam padassati”. ","ja531:73.1":"“Evam te yacamanaya, ","ja531:73.2":"kim na kahami te vaco; ","ja531:73.3":"Vikuddho tyasmi kalyani, ","ja531:73.4":"ma tvam bhayi pabhavati. ","ja531:74.1":"Sabbam te patijanami, ","ja531:74.2":"rajaputti sunohi me; ","ja531:74.3":"Na capi appiyam tuyham, ","ja531:74.4":"kareyyami aham puna. ","ja531:75.1":"Tava kama hi sussoni, ","ja531:75.2":"pahu dukkham titikkhisam; ","ja531:75.3":"Bahum maddakulam hantva, ","ja531:75.4":"nayitum tam pabhavati”. ","ja531:76.1":"“Yojayantu rathe asse, ","ja531:76.2":"nanacitte samahite; ","ja531:76.3":"Atha dakkhatha me vegam, ","ja531:76.4":"vidhamantassa sattavo”. ","ja531:77.1":"“Tanca tattha udikkhimsu, ","ja531:77.2":"ranno maddassantepure; ","ja531:77.3":"Vijambhamanam sihamva, ","ja531:77.4":"photentam digunam bhujam. ","ja531:78.1":"Hatthikkhandhanca aruyha, ","ja531:78.2":"aropetva pabhavatim; ","ja531:78.3":"Sangamam otaritvana, ","ja531:78.4":"sihanadam nadi kuso. ","ja531:79.1":"Tassa tam nadato sutva, ","ja531:79.2":"sihassevitare miga; ","ja531:79.3":"Khattiya vipalayimsu, ","ja531:79.4":"kusasaddabhayattita. ","ja531:80.1":"Hattharoha anikattha, ","ja531:80.2":"rathika pattikaraka; ","ja531:80.3":"Annamannassa chindanti, ","ja531:80.4":"kusasaddabhayattita. ","ja531:81.1":"Tasmim sangamasisasmim, ","ja531:81.2":"passitva hatthamanaso; ","ja531:81.3":"Kusassa ranno devindo, ","ja531:81.4":"ada verocanam manim. ","ja531:82.1":"So tam vijitva sangamam, ","ja531:82.2":"laddha verocanam manim; ","ja531:82.3":"Hatthikkhandhagato raja, ","ja531:82.4":"pavekkhi nagaram puram. ","ja531:83.1":"Jivaggaham gahetvana, ","ja531:83.2":"bandhitva satta khattiye; ","ja531:83.3":"Sasurassupanamesi, ","ja531:83.4":"ime te deva sattavo. ","ja531:84.1":"Sabbeva te vasam gata, ","ja531:84.2":"amitta vihata tava; ","ja531:84.3":"Kamam karohi te taya, ","ja531:84.4":"munca va te hanassu va”. ","ja531:85.1":"“Tuyheva sattavo ete, ","ja531:85.2":"na hi te mayha sattavo; ","ja531:85.3":"Tvanneva no maharaja, ","ja531:85.4":"munca va te hanassu va”. ","ja531:86.1":"“Ima te dhitaro satta, ","ja531:86.2":"devakannupama subha; ","ja531:86.3":"Dadahi nesam ekekam, ","ja531:86.4":"hontu jamataro tava”. ","ja531:87.1":"“Amhakanceva tasanca, ","ja531:87.2":"tvam no sabbesamissaro; ","ja531:87.3":"Tvanneva no maharaja, ","ja531:87.4":"dehi nesam yadicchasi”. ","ja531:88.1":"Ekamekassa ekekam, ","ja531:88.2":"ada sihassaro kuso; ","ja531:88.3":"Khattiyanam tada tesam, ","ja531:88.4":"ranno maddassa dhitaro. ","ja531:89.1":"Pinita tena labhena, ","ja531:89.2":"tuttha sihassare kuse; ","ja531:89.3":"Sakaratthani payimsu, ","ja531:89.4":"khattiya satta tavade. ","ja531:90.1":"Pabhavatinca adaya, ","ja531:90.2":"manim verocanam subham; ","ja531:90.3":"Kusavatim kuso raja, ","ja531:90.4":"agamasi mahabbalo. ","ja531:91.1":"Tyassu ekarathe yanta, ","ja531:91.2":"pavisanta kusavatim; ","ja531:91.3":"Samana vannarupena, ","ja531:91.4":"nannamannatirocisum. ","ja531:92.1":"Mata puttena sangacchi, ","ja531:92.2":"ubhayo ca jayampati; ","ja531:92.3":"Samagga te tada asum, ","ja531:92.4":"phitam dharanimavasunti. ","ja531:93.1":"Kusajatakam pathamam. "}